<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="behind-adv">behind <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'haɪnd/    美 /bɪ'haɪnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在后；向后：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My brother went in front and I walked behind. 
弟弟在前面走，我在他后面跟着。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>落后；慢；迟：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve got behind with my homework. 
我的家庭作业落下了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They are three weeks behind with the rent. 
他们已经拖欠了3个星期的房租。</p></div></div>